description: In this video, I show you how to make vegan pate. This is my most favourite veggie pate ever: Vegan Mushroom & Walnut Pate! Not only is this recipe delicious but this makes for a great vegan appetizer for a party. Make this vegetarian pate, pop it in the fridge, and when you're ready to head out to the party, just grab the vegan mushroom pate along with a loaf of crusty bread or a box of crackers and boom! Delicious party appetized complete. Disclaimer: This video description contains affiliate links. As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases
name: Vegan Mushroom & Walnut Pâté
